<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The top 10 is an issues list.  Issues are class enhancements, bugs, or anything else.  The top 10 is also a feedback on what bards feel is important at the current time.<br>
 <br>
Honestly, I don't think any new features will be added to bards until OoW comes out (such as song or melee improvements) unless it is something game breaking today.<br>
 <br>
Just because items are bugs doesnt mean they are top priority to get fixed.  By including them with the rest of our issues, they may gain the attention they are due (think Jamfest broken for years).<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Let me expand on that by saying the song lands/drops issue is a bug.  A lot of bards will claim that it should be our #1 issue.  Who am I to say it's not an issue?<br>
<br>
As far as taunt goes, I don't want to see it added.  If it does make the top 10 list, I suspect the game designers to shoot it down right away.  But, stranger things have happened. <p><center>
