<br>
Hell, a level 15 mez that works, I would have loved that when I was 15!!!<br>
<br>
At the higher levels taunting for a bard really changes the class.  The ability to consistently taunt and gain agro, then to SoD or Fade to lose agro...I just see alot of power here that I might find some uses for that I shouldnt.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
Now for my needs, and less face it, eq is about ME!!!  I would like warrior AoE taunt.  For those of you who dont know it is a massive aoe taunt that is useable every 15 mins.  Why?<br>
<br>
1.) Gives me the opportunity to be the hero<br>
2.) Hey im a bard I like to click stuff<br>
3.) I need more aas to get<br>
<br>
<br>
If you think about it, there are times when if you could just grab agro for a minute you can save your raid, group, of some knucklehead soloing a mamoth next to the ef camp who is expecting to be bailed out if he gets into trouble.  It would also give me a chance to be turned into mush instead of sitting in the corner faded watching teammates die.<br>
